text: Sandrine Mazetier (born 16 December 1966 in Rodez, Aveyron) is a member of the National Assembly of France. She represents the city of Paris, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:People from Rodez Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Women members of the National Assembly (France) Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:21st-century French women politicians
title: Sandrine Mazetier
